    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.cos((wp.cos(v0 + 0.83) * (v1 + 0.52 / v2 + 0.13)))
    tmp = 0.40
    v0 = (0.87 - wp.exp(wp.sin(tmp + 0.82)))
    v0 = v2
    v1 = ((v2 * (v2 + 0.74 - v2 + 0.54)) * (wp.cos(tmp + 0.89) / tmp))
    v0 = v0
    tmp = (0.25 + wp.cos(v2))
    data[tid] = v0
